import {Component, OnInit} from '@angular/core'; import {Item} from "../../model/item"; import {ItemService} from "../../service/item.service"; @Component({ selector: 'app-item', templateUrl: './item.component.html', styleUrls: ['./item.component.css'] }) export class ItemComponent implements OnInit { items: Item[] = [ { id: 1, price: 120, size: 100, type: 'redőny', colour: 'white' }, { id: 2, price: 120, size: 100, type: 'reluxa', colour: 'green' }, ] constructor(private itemService: ItemService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.items; } }
